:{{DIcon}} I'm just here for a chat...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501030904: Config/Level/Mission/5010309/Act/Act501030904.json-->
::'''Lynx:''' Sure, I don't have any research tasks today. What do you wanna talk about?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501030904_75-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501030904_75-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} So, you're an extreme environments explorer?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030954-->
:::'''Lynx:''' Yup, I'm a member of the Belobog Snow Plains research team.
:::'''Lynx:''' You probably haven't heard of this organization... Our job got called off during Supreme Guardian Cocolia's tenure, and we faded out of the public eye.
:::'''Lynx:''' But to tell you the truth, we used to go on unauthorized expeditions into the Snow Plains from time to time back then...
:::'''Lynx:''' ...Please don't tell Lady Bronya though. She might get upset &mdash; even though our work now have her blessings.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What's your relationship with the Landau family?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030959-->
:::'''Lynx:''' Well... we don't always see eye to eye, but we're not standing eyeball to eyeball, either.
:::'''Lynx:''' I really like hanging out with my sister. She's so cheerful and is so talented in so many things. I admire that about her.
:::'''Lynx:''' As for my big brother... He's hardworking and extremely righteous... I just wish he didn't worry about me so much.
:::'''Lynx:''' Please... don't mention this to anyone, especially not Serval. She'd get all puffed up.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What's your relationship with Pela?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030964-->
:::'''Lynx:''' She's a good friend of mine. We go way back to our days at the Belobog Cadet School.
:::'''Lynx:''' The first time we met was at the school library. At the time, I happened to pick up her unfinished writing, something like ''Tales'', and returned it to her.
:::'''Lynx:''' I was pretty surprised to find out that she was a fan of ''Tales'' too, so I was curious about her opinion on it... But Pela was so shy that she didn't really say anything.
:::'''Lynx:''' Later on... we met again in Serval's band.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You're a member of the band, right?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030969-->
:::'''Lynx:''' Yeah, I'm the keyboard player.
:::'''Lynx:''' Dunn was the keyboard player for Mechanical Fever before I joined, but he got caught up in military duties after graduation and had to leave the band, so I filled in.
:::'''Lynx:''' But from what I heard, there was actually another member before me, a bass player I think? But then they just disappeared, and I heard they had some connection with my sister and Madam Cocolia...
:::'''Lynx:''' ...But these are just baseless rumors, and I don't really know the details. So, don't take this wild story too seriously.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have any more questions.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030974-->
:::'''Lynx:''' Hmm, yeah. Feel free to come to me if you have any more questions.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_501030904-->
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Then I'll leave you to your research.
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501030905: Config/Level/Mission/5010309/Act/Act501030905.json-->
::'''Lynx:''' So long, (Trailblazer). I wish you a smooth ride ahead.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
